CDFglobalAttributes.TEXT: THEMIS Ground Based Observatory part of the THEMIS GBO effort. The All-Sky-Imagers (ASI) take white lght images of the overhead sky. N-S Keograms are generated by combining the North-Southcross section of the image from each UT time into a single image with UT time as x-axis.
